<h4 class='bluish'>1. Panel Basics:</h4>
<div class='row'>
	<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-offset-1">
		<p>Panels allow you to organize your content into visible boxes. The four 
		most important divs contain the classes 'panel panel-default', 
		'panel-heading', 'panel-body' and 'panel-footer'. The div with 
		class='panel panel-default' contains the other three divs. </p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class='row'>
	<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-offset-1 black-text">
		<br>
